Two.

795
00:48:37,420 --> 00:48:38,582
One.

796
00:48:39,506 --> 00:48:42,425
[Section E cheering]

797
00:48:49,474 --> 00:48:52,227
- Why are you blushing?
- That's not allowed here.

798
00:48:53,685 --> 00:48:55,698
- Your face is turning red.
- "Turning red,” as if!

799
00:48:58,588 --> 00:48:59,588
Yuri.

800
00:49:06,372 --> 00:49:08,262
You're being called to
the guidance office, Jay.

801
00:49:08,287 --> 00:49:09,287
Me?

802
00:49:09,312 --> 00:49:11,115
- Yes.
- Huh?

803
00:49:11,513 --> 00:49:12,513
That’s what they said.

804
00:49:35,579 --> 00:49:36,622
Good morning.

805
00:49:37,259 --> 00:49:39,151
- Have a seat.
- You were calling for me, ma'am?

806
00:49:39,151 --> 00:49:40,602
Yes, hold on.

807
00:49:45,774 --> 00:49:49,778
You need to get the signature of
your previous school's counselor.

808
00:49:50,570 --> 00:49:52,197
At my old school?

809
00:49:53,198 --> 00:49:54,198
Why?

810
00:49:54,532 --> 00:49:57,953
The records that they gave us
back then were incomplete.

811
00:49:58,161 --> 00:50:01,915
We kept calling them,
but they always said,

812
00:50:01,915 --> 00:50:03,125
"We will call you back."

813
00:50:05,210 --> 00:50:06,295
My records?

814
00:50:10,256 --> 00:50:12,718
What will happen if
I don't get them signed?

815
00:50:13,841 --> 00:50:14,841
Well,

816
00:50:16,334 --> 00:50:17,544
you won't be able to graduate.

817
00:50:20,392 --> 00:50:22,018
<i>I don't want to go back there.</i>

818
00:50:22,644 --> 00:50:24,771
<i>What if I run into Cyrus?</i>

819
00:50:26,106 --> 00:50:28,525
It probably isn't much
of a hassle for you.

820
00:50:28,900 --> 00:50:31,403
Especially since your
retreat is next week.

821
00:50:32,070 --> 00:50:35,031
It will be held near
your old school.

822
00:50:35,782 --> 00:50:37,660
I hope you can get
this signed by then.

823
00:50:38,284 --> 00:50:40,704
I will just inform
your adviser about it.

824
00:50:40,704 --> 00:50:42,747
So they'll allow
you to leave, okay?

825
00:50:44,156 --> 00:50:45,156
Okay.

826
00:50:57,345 --> 00:50:59,557
How long do you plan
to fool, Jay, huh?

827
00:51:01,933 --> 00:51:03,560
Yeah!

828
00:51:03,661 --> 00:51:04,661
Wow!

829
00:51:04,686 --> 00:51:07,063
You're all bonding
with Jay like you don't

830
00:51:07,063 --> 00:51:10,984
[Section E fighting]

831
00:51:14,612 --> 00:51:16,532
What's going on?!

832
00:51:17,574 --> 00:51:19,702
What’s going on?
Why are you fighting?!

833
00:51:25,123 --> 00:51:27,083
So, no one's going to speak up?

834
00:52:29,403 --> 00:52:30,403
Tell me,

835
00:52:30,855 --> 00:52:32,690
what were you
all fighting about?

836
00:52:32,816 --> 00:52:33,983
Just tell her already!

837
00:52:33,983 --> 00:52:35,485
Shut up! Stop interfering!

838
00:52:35,510 --> 00:52:37,278
Damn it, you're just making
things harder for Ci-N.

839
00:52:37,278 --> 00:52:38,278
Nice room.

840
00:52:38,293 --> 00:52:39,336
What are you doing here?

841
00:52:39,336 --> 00:52:40,699
So you and Keifer
are together now.

842
00:52:40,994 --> 00:52:41,994
What about Yuri?

843
00:52:43,413 --> 00:52:44,706
He wouldn't hope.

844
00:52:45,457 --> 00:52:47,250
If you weren't giving him hope.

845
00:52:47,334 --> 00:52:49,086
Wow!

846
00:52:49,086 --> 00:52:50,754
Look who’s talking.

847
00:52:50,879 --> 00:52:52,005
Who hurt him first, huh?

848
00:52:52,005 --> 00:52:53,131
Really, coming from you?

849
00:52:53,131 --> 00:52:54,966
Camping! Camping!

850
00:52:55,064 --> 00:52:56,065
Camp is rock, baby!

851
00:52:56,273 --> 00:52:57,858
Section E, is that you?

852
00:52:57,858 --> 00:53:00,482
[Section E cheering]

853
00:53:00,507 --> 00:53:03,535
Guys, 3, 2, 1.

854
00:53:04,761 --> 00:53:05,761
Hey, Sir!

855
00:53:05,804 --> 00:53:07,139
Jay-jay, is that you?

856
00:53:07,139 --> 00:53:08,557
Oh no, this is just a hologram.

857
00:53:08,557 --> 00:53:10,725
Cyrus is your boyfriend, right?

858
00:53:11,226 --> 00:53:12,686
He's back in school again.

859
00:53:14,187 --> 00:53:16,189
And nice to see
you here, Jay-jay.

860
00:53:16,189 --> 00:53:17,357
Hey don't leave,

861
00:53:17,357 --> 00:53:18,775
I'm still talking to you.

862
00:53:18,775 --> 00:53:19,775
Cyrus!

863
00:53:19,985 --> 00:53:21,073
It hurts, doesn't it?

864
00:53:21,486 --> 00:53:22,529
Let go of me!

865
00:53:23,071 --> 00:53:24,906
I really, really missed you.

866
00:53:24,906 --> 00:53:26,366
No one's going to help you.

867
00:53:26,700 --> 00:53:28,118
This is it, you're dead!

